  description: "concurrent.futures.as_completed function identity checks in cfwait191 namespace — as_completed.__name__=='as_completed' (len=12: 'as_completed'=12; yields futures as they complete from an iterable, not in submission order); as_completed.__module__=='concurrent.futures._base' (len=24: 'concurrent'=10+'.'=1+'futures'=7+'.'=1+'_base'=5=24; defined in the private _base submodule alongside wait and the Future class); as_completed.__qualname__=='as_completed' (len=12; qualname equals name for a module-level generator function); as_completed.__name__ (12) == as_completed.__qualname__ (12) — module-level function; verified with Python 3.14.3"
